{"title_page": "Pradeep John", "text_new": "{{copy edit|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|weather blogger}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| honorific-suffix   = Independent Weatherman\n| name = Pradeep John\n| image =\n| birth_name = \n| birth_date = {{Birth year and age|1982}}\n| birth_place = Melpuram, Pacode,<br>[[Kanyakumari District]]\n| nationality = [[India|Indian]]\n| education = {{Plainlist| \n* [[Sathyabama University]] ([[B.E]])  \n* [[Madras University]] ([[Master of Business Administration|M.B.A]]) \n }} \n| other_names = \n| years_active = \n| known_for = \n| signature = \n| office = \n}}\n\n'''Pradeep John''', popularly known as '''Tamil Nadu Weatherman''',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dtnext.in/News/TamilNadu/2018/10/01044140/1090518/Fishermen-panic-as-Windy-predicts-cyclone.vpf|title= Fishermen panic as \u2018Windy\u2019 predicts cyclone| work=dtnext.in|accessdate=1 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/chennai/2019/jun/20/will-rains-continue-in-chennai-tamil-nadu-weatherman-comes-out-with-the-answer-1992868.html|title= Will rains continue in Chennai? Tamil Nadu Weatherman comes out with the answer| work=newindianexpress.com|accessdate=20 June 2019}}</ref> is an Indian self-taught weather expert &  blogger from [[Tamil Nadu]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/tn-weatherman-pradeep-john-receives-inspirational-role-model-award-cii-connect-2019-112452|title= TN weatherman Pradeep John receives Inspirational Role Model Award at CII Connect 2019| work=thenewsminute.com|accessdate=17 November 2019}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chennai/chennai-rain-after-196-days-parts-of-city-receives-showers/articleshow/69873617.cms|title= Chennai rain: After 196 days, parts of city receive showers| work=The Times of India}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://scroll.in/article/858252/meet-pradeep-john-an-obscure-blogger-who-became-tamil-nadus-trusted-weatherman|title=An self-taught weather expert.|last=|first=|date=Nov 19, 2017|website=scroll.in|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> It's not an exaggeration when we say that his forecasts are more closely followed by the people of [[Chennai]] than the forecasts shared by the [[India Meteorological Department]] during the season of monsoon. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.parentcircle.com/article/tamil-nadu-weatherman-pradeep-john-chennai-weather-may-be-hotter-than-usual-this-summer/|title= Chennai Weather: Expert Views From Tamil Nadu Weatherman| work=parentcircle.com}}</ref> His [[blogging]] journey started in 2008 when he began to write about [[weather]] & [[rainfall]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://scroll.in/article/858252/meet-pradeep-john-an-obscure-blogger-who-became-tamil-nadus-trusted-weatherman|title= Meet Pradeep John, an obscure blogger who became Tamil Nadu\u2019s trusted weatherman| work=scroll.in}}</ref> Later in 2014, he made his first [[social media]] presence too. His fame in social media skyrocketed after his accurate predictions during the 2015 [[2015 South India floods|Chennai floods]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thebetterindia.com/111285/tamil-nadu-weatherman-weather-forecasts-facebook/|title= How a Common Man Became TN\u2019s Weatherman, Whose Weather Forecasts Are Trusted by 2 Lakh People| work=thebetterindia.com}}</ref>\n\n==Early life==\nPradeep John was born in the [[Kanyakumari district]] and lives in Chennai now. He grew an interest in weather at a very early age of 12 since he was very much fascinated by the power of nature.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://lbb.in/chennai/tamil-nadu-weather-man-chennai/|title= Take A Rain Check? The Tamil Nadu Weather Man Is Here To Predict Chennai's Forecasts| work=lbb.in}}</ref>  He did his schooling at [[SBOA Matriculation and Higher Secondary School, Chennai | SBOA Matriculation School]] and graduated B.E in Computer science and Engineering from [[Sathyabama University]]. He also holds an MBA in Finance from [[Madras University]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theweekendleader.com/Heroism/2630/the-rain-man.html|title= Rain, rain, don\u2019t go away, weatherman Johnny wants to play| work=theweekendleader.com|accessdate=29 June 2017}}</ref> Pradeep John married Hannah Shalini who is a housewife and the couple has a daughter Laura Abigail.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ritzmagazine.in/tracking-the-weather-by-storm-pradeep-johnby-sanjay-pinto/|title= Tracking the weather by storm! \u2013 Pradeep John By Sanjay Pinto| work=ritzmagazine.in|accessdate=31 May 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nIn 2008 Pradeep John joined India Infoline as a relationship manager.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theweekendleader.com/Heroism/2630/the-rain-man.html|title= Rain, rain, don\u2019t go away, weatherman Johnny wants to play| work=theweekendleader.com|accessdate=29 June 2017}}</ref>  Currently,{{when?|date=April 2020}} he works as a Deputy Manager at Tamil Nadu Urban Infrastructure Financial Services Limited (TNUIFSL).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.livechennai.com/detailnews.asp?newsid=37568|title= A common man to a revered weatherman. Everything you need to know| work=livechennai.com|accessdate=1 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Awards and honours==\n* In 2018 Pride of Tamil Nadu Award - Inspirational Achiever.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/chennai/2018/mar/26/and-the-pride-of-tamil-nadu-award-goes-to-1792825.html|title= And the Pride of Tamil Nadu Award goes to| work=newindianexpress.com|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref>\n* In 2019 CII Connect Award - Inspirational Role Model Award.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/tn-weatherman-pradeep-john-receives-inspirational-role-model-award-cii-connect-2019-112452|title= TN weatherman Pradeep John receives Inspirational Role Model Award at CII Connect 2019| work=thenewsminute.com|accessdate=17 November 2019}}</ref> \n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.facebook.com/tamilnaduweatherman/ Official Facebook]\n* [https://twitter.com/praddy06 Official Twitter]\n\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Indian Tamil academics]]\n[[Category:People from Kanyakumari district]]\n[[Category:Engineers from Tamil Nadu]]\n", "text_old": "{{copy edit|date=April 2020}}\n{{short description|weather blogger}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| honorific-suffix   = Independent Weatherman\n| name = Pradeep John\n| image =\n| birth_name = \n| birth_date = {{Birth year and age|1982}}\n| birth_place = Melpuram, Pacode,<br>[[Kanyakumari District]]\n| nationality = [[India|Indian]]\n| education = {{Plainlist| \n* [[Sathyabama University]] ([[B.E]])  \n* [[Madras University]] ([[Master of Business Administration|M.B.A]]) \n }} \n| other_names = \n| years_active = \n| known_for = \n| signature = \n| office = \n}}\n\n'''Pradeep John''', popularly known as '''Tamil Nadu Weatherman''',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dtnext.in/News/TamilNadu/2018/10/01044140/1090518/Fishermen-panic-as-Windy-predicts-cyclone.vpf|title= Fishermen panic as \u2018Windy\u2019 predicts cyclone| work=dtnext.in|accessdate=1 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/chennai/2019/jun/20/will-rains-continue-in-chennai-tamil-nadu-weatherman-comes-out-with-the-answer-1992868.html|title= Will rains continue in Chennai? Tamil Nadu Weatherman comes out with the answer| work=newindianexpress.com|accessdate=20 June 2019}}</ref> is an Indian weather blogger from [[Tamil Nadu]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/tn-weatherman-pradeep-john-receives-inspirational-role-model-award-cii-connect-2019-112452|title= TN weatherman Pradeep John receives Inspirational Role Model Award at CII Connect 2019| work=thenewsminute.com|accessdate=17 November 2019}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://timeso