ani... First look posters of #Shershaah... Directed by Vishnu Varadhan... Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Shabbir Boxwala, Ajay Shah and Himanshu Gandhi... 3 July 2020 release.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=16 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#f1daf1;\" |'''10'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Sadak 2]]'' || [[Mahesh Bhatt]] || {{hlist|[[Sanjay Dutt]]|[[Pooja Bhatt]]|[[Aditya Roy Kapur]]|[[Alia Bhatt]]}}||[[Vishesh Films]], [[Fox Star Studios]] || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1064740226650664960|title= IT'S OFFICIAL... Fox Star Studios and Vishesh Films join hands... Will collaborate over three films, starting with #Sadak2, directed by Mahesh Bhatt... #Sadak2 stars Sanjay Dutt, Pooja Bhatt, Aditya Roy Kapoor and Alia Bhatt.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=24 February 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1130407357979144192|title=Release date finalized... #Sadak2 to release on 10 July 2020... Stars Sanjay Dutt, Pooja Bhatt, Alia Bhatt and Aditya Roy Kapur... Directed by Mahesh Bhatt... Produced by Mukesh Bhatt... Co-produced by Sakshi Bhatt... Fox Star Studios presentation... Filming has commenced.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=20 May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#f1daf1;\" |'''17'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  ''[[Chehre]]''   \n| Rumi Jaffrey || {{hlist|[[Amitabh Bachchan]]|[[Emraan Hashmi]]|[[Krystle D'Souza]]|[[Rhea Chakraborty]]|[[Siddhanth Kapoor]]|[[Dhritiman Chatterjee]]|[[Annu Kapoor]]|[[Raghubir Yadav]]}}|| Anand Pandit Motion Pictures ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1219484644967473152|title=New release date... #Chehre - starring #AmitabhBachchan and #EmraanHashmi - will now release on 17 July 2020... The change in date is due to a request made by the makers of #GulaboSitabo to avert a clash... #Chehre was earlier releasing on 24 April 