ukla @vivekkrishnani #VijayRaaz #GrushaKapoor #DarshanJariwala @aashishw17|publisher=Sony Pictures on Twitter|accessdate=20 February 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#dbfff8;\" |'''20'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  ''Untitled film''   \n| Vardhan Ketkar || [[Sidharth Malhotra]]  ||[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1235049014208290817|title=IT'S OFFICIAL... #SidharthMalhotra to star in an action thriller [not titled yet]... Will essay double role... Directed by Vardhan Ketkar... Produced by Bhushan Kumar and Murad Khetani... Starts May 2020 in #Delhi... 20 Nov 2020 release.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=4 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/amp/news/bollywood/confirmed-sidharth-malhotra-star-tamil-murder-mystery-thadam-remake-film-release-november-20-2020 |title=CONFIRMED! Sidharth Malhotra to star in Tamil murder mystery Thadam remake, film to release on November 20, 2020|website=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n|- December\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#93CCEA; textcolor:#000;\" |'''D<br />E<br />C'''\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0E0E6;\" |'''4'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Brahmastra (film)|Brahmastra]]''||[[Ayan Mukerji]] || {{hlist|[[Amitabh Bachchan]]|[[Ranbir Kapoor]]|[[Alia Bhatt]]|[[Mouni Roy]]|[[Akkineni Nagarjuna]]}} ||[[Dharma Productions]], [[Fox Star Studios]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1223848892116033538|title=#Brahm\u0101stra: Part One release date finalized: 4 Dec 2020... Stars #AmitabhBachchan, #RanbirKapoor, #AliaBhatt, #Nagarjuna, #MouniRoy... Directed by Ayan Mukerji... Produced by Dharma Productions and Fox Star Studios... Will release in #Hindi, #Tamil, #Telugu, #Kannada, #Malayalam|publisher=|accessdate=2 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DharmaMovies/status/122384