ra (actor)|Sanjay Mishra]]|Shikha Malhotra}} ||Pisceann Pictures\n||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/movie-reviews/kaanchli-life-in-a-slough/movie-review/73982041.cms|title=Kaanchli Life In A Slough Movie Review : Low on content, high on skin show}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#dbfff8;\" |'''14'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  ''[[Love Aaj Kal (2020 film)|Love Aaj Kal]]''   \n| [[Imtiaz Ali (director)|Imtiaz Ali]] || {{hlist|[[Kartik Aaryan]]|[[Sara Ali Khan]]|[[Randeep Hooda]]}}|| Jio Studios, Maddock Films, [[Reliance Entertainment]], Window Seat Films ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1217683227436929024|title=#KartikAaryan and #SaraAliKhan... First look poster of #LoveAajKal... Costars #RandeepHooda and newcomer #ArushiSharma... Directed by Imtiaz Ali... Produced by Dinesh Vijan and Imtiaz Ali... 14 Feb 2020 release. #ValentineDay.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=16 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/RelianceEnt/status/1217684117203980288|title=Meet Veer & Zoe, captured in their element. It's in these simple, candid moments that love plays peekaboo, right? #LoveAajKal|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=16 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#dbfff8;\" |'''21'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  ''[[Bhoot \u2013 Part One: The Haunted Ship]]''|| Bhanu Pratap Singh || {{hlist|[[Vicky Kaushal]]|[[Bhumi Pednekar]]}}||[[Dharma Productions]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1174991071534706688|title=New release date... #Bhoot: Part One - The Haunted Ship to release on 21 Feb 2020... Stars Vicky Kaushal and Bhumi Pednekar... Directed by Bhanu Pratap Singh... Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta and Shashank Khaitan... Zee Studios presentation.|accessdate=20 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |  ''[[Shubh Mangal Zyada Saavdhan]