oge aur darroge, phir se, kyunki wapas aa rahe hai hum #BhoolBhulaiyaa2 lekar!|publisher=|accessdate=19 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1163314811410636800|title=IT'S OFFICIAL... Kartik Aaryan in horror-comedy #BhoolBhulaiyaa2... Directed by Anees Bazmee... Produced by BhushanKumar, Murad Khetani and Krishan Kumar... 31 July 2020 release.|publisher=|accessdate=19 August 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1175270743443034112|title=IT'S OFFICIAL... Kiara Advani roped in for #BhoolBhulaiyaa2... Stars Kartik Aaryan... Directed by Anees Bazmee... Produced by Bhushan Kumar, Murad Khetani and Krishan Kumar... 31 July 2020 release.|publisher=|accessdate=21 September 2019}}</ref>\n|- August\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#7FFFD4; textcolor:#000;\" |'''A<br />U<br />G'''\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#dbfff8;\" |'''14'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Bhuj: The Pride of India]]''|| [[Abhishek Dudhaiya]] ||{{hlist|[[Ajay Devgn]]|[[Sanjay Dutt]]|[[Sonakshi Sinha]]|[[Sharad Kelkar]]|[[Ammy Virk]]|[[Pranitha Subhash]]}}||[[Panorama Studios]], [[T-Series (company)|T-Series]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1109683955156938753|title= Taran Adarsh on Twitter|publisher=|accessdate=24 March 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1114441575856132097|title= Taran Adarsh on Twitter|publisher=|accessdate=7 April 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Attack (2020 film)|Attack]]''|| Lakshya Raj Anand ||{{hlist|[[John Abraham]]|[[Jacqueline Fernandez]]|[[Rakul Preet Singh]]}}||[[Pen India Limited]], JA Entertainment, Ajay Kapoor presentation. ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1200765386368548864|title=#IndependenceDay weekend yet again for John Abraham... #Attack to release on 14 Aug 2020... Stars John Abraham, Jacqueline Fernandez and Rakul Preet... 