mar reunite... Akshay in and as the fearless king Prithviraj Chauhan... Directed by Dr Chandraprakash Dwivedi... Titled #Prithviraj... #Diwali2020 release...|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=9 September 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1195214237057990656|title=IT'S OFFICIAL... Miss World 2017 Manushi Chhillar makes her big screen debut... Paired opposite Akshay Kumar in Yash Raj's historical film #Prithviraj... Manushi will play the role of Sanyogita... Directed by Dr Chandraprakash Dwivedi... Produced by Aditya Chopra... #Diwali2020.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=15 November 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/yrf/status/1195243153260871681|title=Presenting the gorgeous @ManushiChhillar as the ethereal beauty, princess Sanyogita. She debuts opposite superstar @akshaykumar in YRF's first and biggest historical film #Prithviraj directed by #DrChandraprakashDwivedi|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=15 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''Dhaakad''   \n| Razneesh \u2018Razy\u2019 Ghai || [[Kangana Ranaut]] || Sohail Makai Productions, Asylum Films ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DharmaMovies/status/1148423099789922304|title=Kangana Ranaut... New poster of #Dhaakad... Directed by Razneesh 'Razy' Ghai... Produced by Sohel Maklai... Co-produced by Qyuki Digital Media... Filming to commence early next year... #Diwali 2020 release.|website=Twitter.com|accessdate=9 July 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Aankh Micholi (2020 film)|Aankh Micholi]]''   \n| [[Umesh Shukla]] || {{hlist|Abhimanyu Dassani|[[Mrunal Thakur]]|[[Paresh Rawal]]|[[Sharman Joshi]]|[[Divya Dutta]]|[[Abhishek Banerjee (actor)|Abhishek Banerjee]]|[[Darshan Jariwala]]|Grusha Kapoor|[[Vijay Raaz]]}} ||[[Sony Pictures Releasing]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1230348874239414273|title=IT'S OFFICIAL... Sony Pictures Films India and #102NotOut and #OhMyGod director Umesh Shukla 